org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure.impl

Class WorldImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure.impl.WorldImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    World

    public class WorldImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements World
    An implementation of the model object 'World'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Nodes
    • Options
    • Default Security Configuration
    • Default Master Handler Priorities
    • Default Credentials
    • Default Master Customization Profile
    • Default Value Archive Customization Profile
    • Default Driver Password
    • Application Configurations
    • Default Driver Access Credentials
